OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783676986
OL,3,CVan driver charged after highways
OL,4,Cworker dies in M23 crash
OL,6,FA van driver has been charged after a
OL,7,Fhighways worker died in a crash on the
OL,8,FM23 at Crawley on Wednesday (8 July).
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fsouthbound carriageway of the M23 at
OL,12,FJunction 9 just before 1am to a
OL,13,Fcollision between a van and a highways
OL,14,Fworker.
OL,16,FA 65-year-old man from Kent died at
OL,17,Fthe scene. Police said his next of kin
OL,18,Fhave been told.
OL,20,FThe driver of the van was arrested at
OL,21,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
