OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783676986
OL,3,CVan driver charged after highways
OL,4,Cworker dies in M23 crash
OL,6,FVilius Domarkas, 38, of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, was charged the same day with
OL,8,Fcausing death by dangerous driving in
OL,9,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,11,FHe appeared at Crawley Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt on Thursday 9 July and was
OL,13,Fremanded into custody until he is due
OL,14,Fto appear at Lewes Crown Court on 6
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FDetective Sergeant Rob Baldwin said:
OL,18,F"We are continuing to support the
OL,19,Fvictim's family following this tragic
OL,20,Fincident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
